Description:
As an engineer, I want to track pending transactions:

* Once the transaction is validated, I want to track it based on asset and user
* Once the transaction is completed, I need to update my state
* I don’t need to update my state in realtime, instead I can check the status of any known pending transactions at the start of my duty cycle, so that I have the most up to date information before I process any further transactions
